<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="eea">

<head>
    <metal:noborder fill-slot="top_slot"
                 tal:define="dummy python:request.set('disable_border',1)" />
</head>

<body>
<metal:main fill-slot="main"
     tal:define="portal context/@@plone_portal_state/portal;
                 email_from_address portal/email_from_address;
                 isAnon context/@@plone_portal_state/anonymous;">

    <h1 class="documentFirstHeading"
        i18n:translate="">Contact EEA Web Team</h1>

    <div class="documentDescription"
         tal:condition="portal/description"
         tal:content="portal/description"></div>

    <p>You may contact the EEA Web Team for reporting technical issues or in case you want to submit an idea for improvement of the website.</p>
    <ul>
    <li><strong>Technical issues</strong>: <a title="Visit the EEA Forum" href="http://community.eea.europa.eu">Visit the EEA Forum for technical issues or support</a>. Use the category "Technical Topics".
    </li>
    <li><strong>Suggest ideas for improvement</strong>: <a href="javascript:UserVoice.showPopupWidget();" title="Website feedback">Submit your idea or vote an existing idea</a> for website improvements.</li>
    </ul>
    <br><br>
    <p>For questions not related to the website you may <a href="/help/infocentre/enquiries">Ask a question via the Enquiry Service</a></p>
</metal:main>
</body>
</html>
